: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KRBibtPM3kPe1RHwRiacNGbBGck5QX1licnzT69J7gRj1dQ642HyhzYQfibQMHde9LoNoB2FJ9iaroCDjBrZ11mgOLw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KRBibtPM3kPe1RHwRiacNGbBGck5QX1licnknbEbME5xukpicLeS2KVI6zVUYKlW2DbTO9FMQIibSAC12ians6iarfrww/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KRBibtPM3kPe1RHwRiacNGbBGck5QX1licn4KHGKicNuNmia5KpR9tWHbp82R3G0wfjwUlS946106popdUDlqjZtyhQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(122, 68, 66);\">2017是难忘的，回首往昔，2017我们织就了一幅变革与创新的美丽画卷，在征服与挑战中，我们收获着属于我们的那一份荣誉与认同。2018是期待的，展望未来，岁月似歌，2018我们继续擂响跨越与创造的激昂战鼓，在雄心与霸气间，我们要追逐梦想道路上的灿烂与辉煌。</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(122, 68, 66);\">紧接着，株洲市文体广电新闻出版局副局长，株洲市体育总会副主席王建志，湖南省社会体育指导服务中心主任、全国排舞广场舞推广中心湖南省中心主任周光正分别发表讲话，从领导的讲话中我们听到了对我们过去的肯定，但更多的是对我们未来的期许，相信在新的一年，我们会携手新的跨越，再创新的佳绩。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KRBibtPM3kPe1RHwRiacNGbBGck5QX1licn83pttFoia8fXU1W4sgS0GnhdpLBicrupvR9sycAicQqx6LDfzN9h4Ugng/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/KRBibtPM3kPe1RHwRiacNGbBGck5QX1licnEYtv2szKBMSib31sicMrXIZffJWbblEOM84DNzD5QaLnRhRR0PQI